headline: 3 Industrials Stocks We Keep Off Our Radar
summary: Even if they go mostly unnoticed, industrial businesses are the backbone of our country. They are also bound to benefit from a friendlier regulatory environment with the Trump administration, and this excitement has led to a six-month gain of 22.1% for the sector - higher than the S&P 500’s 15.5% return.
